          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Differential cross sections for elastic scattering of",
                " tagged,  monochromatic photons have been measured on",
                " a water target for incident photon energies  between",
                " 21.7  and  27.5  MeV and at scattering angles of 135",
                " and 45 degrees.",
                "These data  are  interpreted  in  terms  of the total",
                " photoabsorption cross section in the region  of  the",
                " giant  dipole  resonance.  The  data  are reasonably",
                " consistent with previous direct measurements of  the",
                " total    photoabsrorption    cross    section    and",
                " inconsistent with more recent determinations of  the",
                " total  cross  section by summing the various partial",
                " cross sections."
              ]
            }
          ],
